title: Basic Channel Collection (1993-2004)
description:
Basic Channel + side projects:

---------------------------------------------

Basic Channel (more or less):

Basic Reshape (Remixes of Paperclip People)
Enforcement
Infinition / Hyperprism
Inversion
Lyot Rmx / Phylyps Rmx
Octagon
Phylyps Trak
Phylyps Trak II
Q 1.1
Quadrant Dub
Radiance


Rhythm & Sound:

Rhythm & Sound
The Versions

Round One to Round Five:

1993-99 Main Street Records

---------------------------------------------

All artists listed above are just the same two people who are in Basic Channel.

Basic Channel and Maurizio are basically the same thing.

Rhythm & Sound are more "traditional" dub made with reggae. Left out their more "popular" releases as R&S to keep the vocals to a minimum. The Versions is the instrumental version of their most popular release, Rhythm & Sound w/ the Artists.

Round One to Round Five are described as house, but it mostly sounds like dub techno to me. Beware, there be vocals here.

---------------------------------------------

All tracks have been "remastered" by me, meaning that long silences at the beginning and end of tracks have been removed.

160kbps mp3
